                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "Of course "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "user",
                                "user_id": "UBS7QANF3"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": " is right that it's total profit that counts, but my experience is that in practice driving up margin even at the cost of volume is usually the right call for maximising total profit. I can't fully justify why - but whenever I try to push volume by reducing margin I end up with less profit overall."
                            }
