                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "user": "UGV299K6H",
        "type": "message",
        "ts": "1614172889.028300",
        "client_msg_id": "bfa59eb7-47a9-4ace-8d7c-40989460673d",
        "text": "I actually tracked this over a number of years by characterising every change to my live betting in terms of whether margin and volume was increased or reduced and the correlation was very strong. It's not that I never increase volume - I just either do it in some way that doesn't compromise margin or I do it very cautiously with careful monitoring and a view to gaining data that will then let me dial up the margin again.",
