        "client_msg_id": "59429e28-eafb-456f-9946-e2b0fa3d13fe",
        "text": "I think that's also why i've been looking at ROI. Pushing more volume from the market is easier said than done, so went for improving my matching \/ removing bad bets and then try again when i have more margin to play with. It felt like a logical approach sacrificing a small amount of profit hopefully in the short term for the long term gains but at the same time choosing a less profitable strategy didn't seem logical.",
