        "text": "It is not a one to one mapping to the trading domain but ml techniques such as support vector regression have a built in concept of “margin” to separate points better and give better out of sample performance. maintaining margin for trading strats to me is similar to how SVR creates bands around training examples to help classify points better. too low of a margin and SVR has high variance. Something similar happens to trading strats",
